SEC. 109. REAUTHORIZATION OF CHESAPEAKE BAY PROGRAM. Section 117 of the Federal Water Pollution Control Act (33 
U.S.C. 1267) is amended by striking subsection (j) and inserting 
the following: 
‘‘(j) AUTHORIZATION OF APPROPRIATIONS.—There are authorized 
to be appropriated to carry out this section— 
‘‘(1) for fiscal year 2021, $90,000,000; 
‘‘(2) for fiscal year 2022, $90,500,000; 
‘‘(3) for fiscal year 2023, $91,000,000; 
‘‘(4) for fiscal year 2024, $91,500,000; and 
‘‘(5) for fiscal year 2025, $92,000,000.’’.

